metadata.name: Unravel People's PENGUINS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's PENGUINS, which represents an inactive state of pPENGUINS. Users can participate in a new Pudgy Penguin acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's PENGUINS as credit. upPENGUINS can be claimed into pPENGUINS when the subscription successfully acquires a new Pudgy Penguin.
